verbose_text: A soluble sulfur oxygenase reductase (SOR) mediates the initial step in the Sdegrees oxidation pathway of aerobically grown cells, a unique enzyme catalyzing the simultaneous Sdegrees oxygenation and disproportionation to sulfite, thiosulfate, and sulfide.
evidence: sulfur oxygenase reductase (SOR) mediates the initial step
